# Ufro InstaPick

## Instantly match physical objects to PMS Colors and design in Adobe Creative Cloud

[Get Instapick (Visit Licensee Site)](https://instapick.ufro.com/#store "Click to Get Instapick (Visit Licensee Site)")

Instapick, a licensed color capture device from Ufro Inc., instantly measures a physical object, matches to the nearest Pantone Matching System (PMS) color, and inserts the color into your design software. This desktop device connects to your computer via Bluetooth and pairs with ColorKing+ software for Mac and PC to add color into Adobe® Creative Cloud® and Expresii® design programs. Instapick is a great color capture option for web and digital designers who prioritize color picking speed in their creative workflow.

- Get an instant Pantone Color added into a design file object
- Device battery can last for 600 days or up to 100,000 color matches
- Includes color matching to all PMS libraries for graphics
- Not compatible with Pantone Connect

